com.pipe42.data.pojos

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pipe42.data.pojos.Project

  • public final class Project
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the Project model object used in the DAO. It defines the Project details themselves and adds together the IDs from other objects that belong to this project.
    Since:
    0.1.0
